{"title":"道路小札","authors":["牛根生"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":11,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路小札"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山西太原重型机器厂  牛根生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵的飞旋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠里的骆驼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌云里的闪电。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动的旋律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"智慧的明眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海里的航标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地的琴弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从心里流出的泉水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把人间的生命浇灌……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁的手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽着美丽的蓝天……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（七）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳抛下的玉带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和理想紧紧相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（八）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步雕刻的珍品，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵设计的图案。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（九）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间留下的影子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史刻下的纪念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（十）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的向导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望的笑脸……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（十一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春蚕吐出的细丝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明纺织的金线……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}